{"tid":288721,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"出嚟工作咗好幾年，有冇人放棄學習？","createTime":"2017-06-18T11:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T15:57:14.000Z","uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45c52a1e3236d720d9709f592b85774f6091fd96","tid":288721,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"自已出嚟做嘢做咗一段時間，人工雖然唔高，只有一萬多，但又唔算最差，工作時間又算穩定，但係自己已經到咗而立之年，卻功業未成，好聽啲叫基層工，難聽啲打份牛工，冇出色冇前途嗰啲。<br />\n唔知係唔係返工返得耐嘅關係，再加上以前接觸嘅人同事，開始覺得學習呢一回事係一件吃力不討好嘅事，總係覺得：「學嚟做乜，都冇用嘅，有時間嘅都做嘢，返到屋企，食吓飯，睇吓電視，上吓網好過，仲學乜撚嘢，嘥心機挨眼睏。」，網上又唔少人都留言：「三張幾仲走去讀書嘅人係硬膠膠嘅，睇吓阿邊個邊個，中學未畢業，出嚟做嚟，做到而家風生水起，一世無憂。」。<br />\n以上嘅說話，我聽到，睇到都都唔少，而自己嘅信念開始動搖，但係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好驚有一天會變成廢中廢老，做一隻不折不扣嘅老油條。"},{"pid":"594dde09988fa38533d89d0e7279b53f160fbfc5","tid":288721,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"想問下大家有冇咁嘅經歷？"},{"pid":"151b8eb8edaffdf20a33ee2b7ca7e13178198325","tid":288721,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"788a9b579a4d2edd62edfea45a62c843b22433e2","tid":288721,"uid":117855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"有錢等於有意義?<br />\n<br />\n應該係掛"},{"pid":"4106a7988ca8e919b983abe924836a6270c581e3","tid":288721,"uid":1576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"想學但冇咩planning <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得個講字"},{"pid":"5f0884b5aab9636af4a571549485dff817c5b4e8","tid":288721,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"想就去喇 有心唔怕遲<br />\n到你十年後 四十幾歲又會loop 呢個問題 到時又會話早知三十幾歲時讀 到五十歲又話四十歲做咩唔讀 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出咗嚟做野 上年畢業<br />\n下年都計劃緊讀個master 增值自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0051d10b8976ac3e8a38de5831c3693d75731b76","tid":288721,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4923a24c2c9e9f9fa8c87bb49080bc8de2f85bad","tid":288721,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"對我嚟講，係出咗嚟做嘢之後，學習咗放棄"},{"pid":"55dcd9b9ce1d3676cccbe076242e046497aa5acc","tid":288721,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我嚟講，係出咗嚟做嘢之後，學習咗放棄</blockquote><br />\n放棄相信大家都有，包括放棄初衷、放棄理想、放棄興趣等。<br />\n但係而家如果要reboot自己先係最困難。"},{"pid":"f9c93d9fff20be1f761ac6191824f49deb868667","tid":288721,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0614df44c78c258bc68889f32573c4829fbdc5fe","tid":288721,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c76868b4b6640fe63b3bbf6f0d53008b3ed5145","tid":288721,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"係讀書料,有心讀既神早發奮讀好書啦<br />\n洗撚出黎做幾年野先返去讀咩"},{"pid":"eba1b10771348902f7bd61e0de66b18633f8d821","tid":288721,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"做過野 讀返書 你會覺得好吃力"},{"pid":"4b37f3ad268101b18d8cda8c37aacc8c739fe13a","tid":288721,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係讀書料,有心讀既神早發奮讀好書啦<br />\n洗撚出黎做幾年野先返去讀咩</blockquote><br />\n但係有目標總好過行屍走肉。<br />\n放工打機、煲劇、上網、嫖賭飲蕩吹，乜都唔使諗當然係開心，但係長時間係咁會好空虛。"},{"pid":"e2fafc8b9022fc5f8eb89dd294c80ff97b7fccdd","tid":288721,"uid":121762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對我嚟講，係出咗嚟做嘢之後，學習咗放棄</blockquote><br />\n放棄相信大家都有，包括放棄初衷、放棄理想、放棄興趣等。<br />\n但係而家如果要reboot自己先係最困難。</blockquote><br />\n小學包尾大班 - 日日顧打機<br />\n中學重學 - 日日返學訓覺淨係顧踢波 (丙組..乙組..初衷、理想、興趣)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhigh dip 又要retake一科 - 第一年仲堅持興趣 之後開始低迷個人開始頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀完出黎做咗一年野 (文職 - 好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n又hea返半年 中間去咗兩次旅行<br />\n其他時間日夜癲倒 晚晚出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次偶然再做返野 轉行地盤做咗兩個月決定讀返書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩做夠一年 讀書目前都OK<br />\n<br />\nreboot自己其實真係幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返真係慶幸自己有捉住個一次偶然<br />\n工作辛苦但我享受其中 種感覺好踏實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無後悔一開始放棄學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025e0342de6bad21a8a1fb1f62b5ad66ba2a9f9a","tid":288721,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"返工好攰, 無動力學習新知識"},{"pid":"fca7d4f1cacfeb0413a772559556b2c633f88f2b","tid":288721,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"你同事無錯，三張幾野，D人一早讀完 phd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9fd43bcfb4a85fecd65edd97b4432a7be2a631","tid":288721,"uid":3896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係讀書料,有心讀既神早發奮讀好書啦<br />\n洗撚出黎做幾年野先返去讀咩</blockquote><br />\n但係有目標總好過行屍走肉。<br />\n放工打機、煲劇、上網、嫖賭飲蕩吹，乜都唔使諗當然係開心，但係長時間係咁會好空虛。</blockquote><br />\n係, 做咗野一年多d, 遲畢業 廿六歲<br />\n冇乜朋友 冇乜興趣, 都諗好唔好去讀master...<br />\n日日返工放工, 放假鳩hea, 好虛耗光陰咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a0620091f0a2855e799def8b70ec8750e9230a","tid":288721,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係讀書料,有心讀既神早發奮讀好書啦<br />\n洗撚出黎做幾年野先返去讀咩</blockquote><br />\n但係有目標總好過行屍走肉。<br />\n放工打機、煲劇、上網、嫖賭飲蕩吹，乜都唔使諗當然係開心，但係長時間係咁會好空虛。</blockquote><br />\n老實講 30歲人仲搵緊一萬幾千 都仲唔進修 等咩？"},{"pid":"40bb6a40ac4874ffd79bf9de980a1abb107b591d","tid":288721,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係讀書料,有心讀既神早發奮讀好書啦<br />\n洗撚出黎做幾年野先返去讀咩</blockquote><br />\n但係有目標總好過行屍走肉。<br />\n放工打機、煲劇、上網、嫖賭飲蕩吹，乜都唔使諗當然係開心，但係長時間係咁會好空虛。</blockquote><br />\n老實講 30歲人仲搵緊一萬幾千 都仲唔進修 等咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等老d既時候比人淘汰"},{"pid":"9fd6e4d8870d334f6dcda6506b153df498e82c78","tid":288721,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"香港口號淨係識進修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850c2350297c6a09d032e3455352fb27757e070b","tid":288721,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"有同感"},{"pid":"e89e7a89657ab110ce517d463c8a2af2e631eca8","tid":288721,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"係首先知自己想要啲乜，再搵書嚟講（如果需要）<br />\n<br />\n盲目搵書讀無用㗎"},{"pid":"ff5f2953070e266ec958c6f254e1b398dca245b2","tid":288721,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f43f78c60dc8fbff4ba46cc4c743bf991424bfd","tid":288721,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}